author: Coffeezilla
description:
A massive banking failure has frozen users funds for almost a year. Nobody has accepted blame, lawsuits are flying--I decided to investigate but what I found seemed hopeless. 

Ultimately the victims kept me going. They trusted FDIC insured banks but now their money has vanished. Up to $96 million dollars may be missing, and I tried to get answers.
